filedrop - host a simple file upload form that notifies you when someone you've allowed uploads a file

Instructions:

Install filedrop directory somewhere.

Configure Apache to see the directory.

  Alias /filedrop /path/to/filedrop
  <Directory /path/to/filedrop>
    AllowOverride All
    Allow from All
  </Directory>

# configure filedrop settings
cd /path/to/filedrop
cp .htaccess.sample .htaccess
